title: Population of the Netherlands 2019 , by age
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of inhabitants. In total the number of data points it has is 5.
Overall Number of inhabitants has decreased over the Year.
Number of inhabitants is roughly constant from 0_-_20_years to 20_-_40_years, and lastly slightly decreasing from 20_-_40_years to 80_years_and_older.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 40_-_65_years and 65_-_80_years.
Maximum Number of inhabitants, about 5866334.0 was reported at Year 40_-_65_years
Minimum Number of inhabitants about 798820.0 was reached at Year 80_years_and_older
